,{"id":37235,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/10\/27\/umar-dua-salat-ala-nabi\/","url_meta":{"origin":34632,"position":2},"title":"Umar on Dua: Supplication held back until the Prophet is blessed","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 27, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Sa\u2019id ibn al-Musayyib reported: Umar ibn al-Khattab, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cVerily, the supplication is suspended between the heavens and the earth. Nothing ascends from it until you send blessings upon your Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 486 Grade: Sahih li ghayrihi\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33014,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/08\/01\/what-to-say-final-tashahhud\/","url_meta":{"origin":34632,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Tashahhud: What to say at end of prayer","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 1, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Ka\u2019b ibn \u2018Urjah reported: We asked, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, how do we send blessings upon you and the people of the house? Allah has taught us how to send peace upon you.\u201d The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cSay: O Allah, send grace upon Muhammad and\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":37655,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2022\/01\/19\/dua-tawhid-ibrahim\/","url_meta":{"origin":3463